edu.doane.dugal.samples.functions

Class BinaryDeJong02

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.doane.dugal.samples.functions.BinaryDeJong02
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Problem

    public class BinaryDeJong02
extends java.lang.Object
implements Problem
    Sample DEA application: DeJong's second function, using binary chromosomes. Maximize the function f_2 = 100 \left( x_1^2 - x_2 \right)^2 + \left( 1 - x_1 \right)^2 (This is negation of the standard DeJong's second function, since the DEA framework maximizes instead of minimizes.)
    Version:
    03/25/2016
    Author:
    Mark M. Meysenburg
